{"tid":1185581,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"華拉度列7人疑打假波　賽會查煞科戰兩失球","createTime":"2019-06-04T10:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T12:35:21.000Z","uid":10338,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c8f53708f8555330f7c73a2890c35bbaf67ecacc","tid":1185581,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"西甲假波醜聞再有新進展，華拉度列據報有7名球員被收買，在煞科戰對華倫西亞操控賽果，賽會正作調查。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙警方早前帶走7人問話，包括前拉斯彭馬斯前鋒卡路士艾蘭達。西班牙《世界報》發放其一段錄音，指他作為中間人，曾說：「下注1萬歐元（約8.83萬港元），你會得到2萬歐元。兄弟，華倫西亞上、下半場都要贏，可以嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n報道又指出，他曾說過「7人被收買，沒有更多」。華拉度列管理層，如班主朗拿度等並不知情。最終煞科戰前已篤定護級的華拉度列，因傑高奧利華斯及魯賓艾卡利斯的失誤，上、下半場各失1球而落敗，作客贏波的華倫則保住第4，出戰來季歐聯。<br />\n<br />\n西假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c20c621087bb4d7d948e893ede73077d1a4b53","tid":1185581,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:50:44.000Z","msg":"西假意假風水輪流轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02588aeb8fbbf4588d6fed4bd68fd0df5ce56cb7","tid":1185581,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52c20c621087bb4d7d948e893ede73077d1a4b53","tid":1185581,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:50:44.000Z","msg":"西假意假風水輪流轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n